race.comment: BIG TRUCKER (2) scored a 0.8 lengths win this course and distance last time in a personal Best Time (17.05) and also clocked one of the quickest wins on the card. Has the ability and expected to go close again. ROOSTER LEGS (1) comes off an average performance last start when eighth at Warrnambool over 390m behind Undercover Guy (22.92) in a Grade 4/5. Expected to feature in the finish. ASSUME KEALY (8) latest effort finished 7th on August 29 over 300m at this track behind Devil In Me beaten 5 lengths (17.54) in a Grade 5. Rates a key chance on best figures. HOT CROSS (3) is not to be discarded.
